datasets.name: Really Grate Tree Project
datasets.description: Sidewalk trees are notoriously short lived with a reduced canopy. They grow in the places we need trees the most: high density hardscapes. The Really Grate Tree Project is working to understand how these trees survive and experiment with methods to improve their growth.
